.TH CLDR-VIEWER 1 "2026-02-15" "Daniel Nylander" "CLDR Viewer Manual"
.SH NAME
cldr-viewer - Browse and compare Unicode CLDR locale data
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B cldr-viewer
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBcldr-viewer\fR is a GTK4/Adwaita application for browsing and comparing Unicode CLDR locale data across locales. It displays date formats, month names, weekdays, currencies, units, and time zone names per locale. Features include side-by-side locale comparison, missing translation highlighting, coverage percentages per category, search and filter, and local caching with 24-hour TTL.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-help
Show help message and exit.
.SH KEYBOARD SHORTCUTS
.TP
.B Ctrl+Q
Quit the application
.TP
.B F5
Refresh the current data
.TP
.B Ctrl+/
Show keyboard shortcuts dialog
.TP
.B Ctrl+E
Export current view to CSV or JSON format
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/cldr-viewer/
Configuration files.
.TP
.I ~/.cache/cldr-viewer/
Cached data.
